item.title: Nico Holmberg
item.description:
Doctoral Student Computational Quantum Chemistry Aalto University Espoo, Finland                  
Biography Nico Holmberg graduated M.Sc. (Tech) in Chemical Engineering at Aalto University in December 2014, where he subsequently began his doctoral studies. Nico is not your typical chemist working in a laboratory with brightly colored liquids, fancy automated equipment, or anything you might expect from popular TV shows.
